Welcome to cipher day!
For this challenge, you need to write a program that will take the scrambled words from this post, and compare them against the attached word list to unscramble them.
For bonus points, sort the words by length when you are finished. Post your programs and/or subroutines!
Here are your words to de-scramble:

mkeart
sleewa
edcudls
iragoge
usrlsle
nalraoci
nsdeuto
amrhat
inknsy
iferkna

